, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\\\"><div class=\\\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\\\"><p class=\\\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\\\" style=\\\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\\\">They are designed to prevent China\'s military from importing advanced semiconductors or equipment.<\\/p><\\/div><\\/div><div data-component=\\\"text-block\\\" class=\\\"ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\\\" style=\\\"margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\\\"><div class=\\\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\\\"><p class=\\\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\\\" style=\\\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\\\">Nvidia\\u00a0<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/d18rn0p25nwr6d.cloudfront.net\\/CIK-0001045810\\/6314522a-929c-470d-b67c-23fa99238516.pdf\\\" class=\\\"ssrcss-k17ofw-InlineLink e1kn3p7n0\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: none; border-left: 0px; border-image: initial; font-styl