: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\\\"><\\/div><div data-component=\\\"text-block\\\" class=\\\"ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\\\" style=\\\"margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\\\"><div class=\\\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\\\"><p class=\\\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\\\" style=\\\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\\\">The Semiconductor Industry Association, which represents 99% of the US semiconductor industry by revenue, said in\\u00a0<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.semiconductors.org\\/sia-statement-on-new-export-controls-2\\/\\\" class=\\\"ssrcss-k17ofw-InlineLink e1kn3p7n0\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: none; border-left: 0px; border-image: initial; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-set