nt-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: underline 1px rgb(138, 140, 142); text-decoration-skip-ink: none; text-underline-offset: 0.25em;\\\">has announced<\\/a><b class=\\\"ssrcss-hmf8ql-BoldText e5tfeyi3\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\\\">&nbsp;new restrictions on exports of advanced chips to China, including two made-for-China chips from Nvidia.<\\/b><\\/font><\\/p><\\/div><\\/div><div data-component=\\\"text-block\\\" class=\\\"ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\\\" style=\\\"margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem;\\\"><div class=\\\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\\\"><p class=\\\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\\\" style=\\\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\\\">US chip stocks fell as the curbs also hit Advanced Micro Devices and Intel.<\\/p><\\/div><\\/div><div data-component=\\\"text-block\\\" class=\\\"ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\\\" style=\\\"margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem;\\\"><div class=\\\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\\\"><p class=\\\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\\\" style=\\\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\\\">The curbs are aimed at closing loopholes that became apparent after&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.bbc.com\\/news\\/business-63175527\\\" class=\\\"ssrcss-k17ofw-InlineLink e1kn3p7n0\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: none; border-left: 0px; border-image: initial; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: underline 1px rgb(138, 140, 142); text-decoration-skip-ink: none; text-underline-offset: 0.25em;\\\">the US announced export curbs on chips last October<\\/a>.<\\/p><\\/div><\\/div><div data-component=\\\"text-block\\\" class=\\\"ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\\\" style=\\\"margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem;\\\"><div class=\\\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\\\"><p class=\\\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\\\" style=\\\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\\\">They are designed to prevent China\'s military from importing advanced semiconductors or equipment.<\\/p><\\/div><\\/div><div data-component=\\\"text-block\\\" class=\\\"ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\\\" style=\\\"margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem;\\\"><div class=\\\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\\\"><p class=\\\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\\\" style=\\\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\\\">Nvidia&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/d18rn0p25nwr6d.cloudfront.net\\/CIK-0001045810\\/6314522a-929c-470d-b67c-23fa99238516.pdf\\\" class=\\\"ssrcss-k17ofw-InlineLink e1kn3p7n0\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: none; border-left: 0px; border-image: initial; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: underline 1px rgb(138, 140, 142); text-decoration-skip-ink: none; text-underline-offset: 0.25em;\\\">has said in a filing<\\/a>&nbsp;that the new export restrictions will block sales of two high-end artificial intelligence chips it created for the Chinese market - A800 and H800. It said that one of its gaming chips will also be blocked.<\\/p><\\/div><\\/div><div data-component=\\\"text-block\\\" class=\\\"ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\\\" style=\\\"margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem;\\\"><div class=\\\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\\\"><p class=\\\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\\\" style=\\\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\\\">Although the curbs also affect other chip makers, analysts believe Nvidia will be hit the hardest because China accounts for up to 25% of its revenues from data centre chip sales. Nvidia\'s shares, which are considered a star stock, fell by as much as 4.7% in the wake of the announcement.<\\/p><\\/div><\\/div><div id=\\\"piano-inline1\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\\\"><\\/div><div data-component=\\\"text-block\\\" class=\\\"ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\\\" style=\\\"margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem;\\\"><div class=\\\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\\\"><p class=\\\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\\\" style=\\\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\\\">The Semiconductor Industry Association, which represents 99% of the US semiconductor industry by revenue, said in&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.semiconductors.org\\/sia-statement-on-new-export-controls-2\\/\\\" class=\\\"ssrcss-k17ofw-InlineLink e1kn3p7n0\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: none; border-left: 0px; border-image: initial; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: underline 1px rgb(138, 140, 142); text-decoration-skip-ink: none; text-underline-offset: 0.25em;\\\">a statement<\\/a>&nbsp;that the new measures are \\\"overly broad\\\" and \\\"risk harming the US semiconductor ecosystem without advancing national security as they encourage overseas customers to look elsewhere\\\".<\\/p><\\/div><\\/div><div data-component=\\\"text-block\\\" class=\\\"ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\\\" style=\\\"margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem;\\\"><div class=\\\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\\\"><p class=\\\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\\\" style=\\\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\\\">A spokesperson for the Chinese embassy also said that it \\\"firmly opposes\\\" the new restrictions, which also target Iran and Russia and go into effect in 30 days.<\\/p><\\/div><\\/div><div data-component=\\\"text-block\\\" class=\\\"ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\\\" style=\\\"margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem;\\\"><div class=\\\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\\\"><p class=\\\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\\\" style=\\\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\\\">Two months ago, China retaliated by&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.bbc.com\\/news\\/business-66118831\\\" class=\\\"ssrcss-k17ofw-InlineLink e1kn3p7n0\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: none; border-left: 0px; border-image: initial; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: underline 1px rgb(138, 140, 142); text-decoration-skip-ink: none; text-underline-offset: 0.25em;\\\">restricting exports of two materials<\\/a>, gallium and germanium, which are key to the semiconductor industry.<\\/p><\\/div><\\/div><div data-component=\\\"text-block\\\" class=\\\"ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\\\" style=\\\"margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem;\\\"><div class=\\\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\\\"><p class=\\\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\\\" style=\\\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\\\">China is by far the biggest player in the global supply chain of gallium and germanium. It produces 80% of the world\'s gallium and 60% of germanium, according to the Critical Raw Materials Alliance (CRMA) industry body.<\\/p><\\/div><\\/div><div data-component=\\\"text-block\\\" class=\\\"ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\\\" style=\\\"margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem;\\\"><div class=\\\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\\\"><p class=\\\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\\\" style=\\\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\\\">The materials are \\\"minor metals\\\", meaning that they are not usually found on their own in nature, and are often the by-product of other processes.<\\/p><\\/div><\\/div><div data-component=\\\"text-block\\\" class=\\\"ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\\\" style=\\\"margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem;\\\"><div class=\\\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\\\"><p class=\\\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\\\" style=\\\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\\\">Besides the US, both Japan and the Netherlands - which is home to key chip equipment maker ASML - have also imposed chip technology export restrictions on China.<\\/p><\\/div><\\/div><div id=\\\"piano-inline2\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\\\"><\\/div><div data-component=\\\"text-block\\\" class=\\\"ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\\\" style=\\\"margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem;\\\"><div class=\\\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\\\"><p class=\\\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\\\" style=\\\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\\\">The constant tit-for-tat between the world\'s two biggest economies has raised concerns over the rise of so-called \\\"resource nationalism\\\" when governments hoard critical materials to exert influence over other countries.<\\/p><\\/div><\\/div>\"},\"old\":{\"content\":\"<div data-component=\\\"text-block\\\" class=\\\"ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\\\" style=\\\"margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem;\\\"><div class=\\\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\\\"><p class=\\\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\\\" style=\\\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color: rgb(206, 198, 206);\\\"><b class=\\\"ssrcss-hmf8ql-BoldText e5tfeyi3\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\\\">The Biden administration&nbsp;<\\/b><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.bis.doc.gov\\/index.php\\/about-bis\\/newsroom\\/2082?ref=upstract.com\\\" class=\\\"ssrcss-k17ofw-InlineLink e1kn3p7n0\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: none; border-left: 0px; border-image: initial; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: underline 1px rgb(138, 140, 142); text-decoration-skip-ink: none; text-underline-offset: 0.25em;\\\">has announced<\\/a><b class=\\\"ssrcss-hmf8ql-BoldText e5tfeyi3\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\\\">&nbsp;new restrictions on exports of advanced chips to China, including two made-for-China chips from Nvidia.<\\/b><\\/span><\\/p><\\/div><\\/div><div data-component=\\\"text-block\\\" class=\\\"ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\\\" style=\\\"margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem;\\\"><div class=\\\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\\\"><p class=\\\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\\\" style=\\\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color: rgb(206, 198, 206);\\\">US chip stocks fell as the curbs also hit Advanced Micro Devices and Intel.<\\/span><\\/p><\\/div><\\/div><div data-component=\\\"text-block\\\" class=\\\"ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\\\" style=\\\"margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem;\\\"><div class=\\\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\\\"><p class=\\\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\\\" style=\\\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color: rgb(206, 198, 206);\\\">The curbs are aimed at closing loopholes that became apparent after&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.bbc.com\\/news\\/business-63175527\\\" class=\\\"ssrcss-k17ofw-InlineLink e1kn3p7n0\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: none; border-left: 0px; border-image: initial; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: underline 1px rgb(138, 140, 142); text-decoration-skip-ink: none; text-underline-offset: 0.25em;\\\">the US announced export curbs on chips last October<\\/a>.<\\/span><\\/p><\\/div><\\/div><div data-component=\\\"text-block\\\" class=\\\"ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\\\" style=\\\"margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem;\\\"><div class=\\\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\\\"><p class=\\\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\\\" style=\\\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color: rgb(206, 198, 206);\\\">They are designed to prevent China\'s military from importing advanced semiconductors or equipment.<\\/span><\\/p><\\/div><\\/div><div data-component=\\\"text-block\\\" class=\\\"ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\\\" style=\\\"margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem;\\\"><div class=\\\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\\\"><p class=\\\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\\\" style=\\\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color: rgb(206, 198, 206);\\\">Nvidia&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/d18rn0p25nwr6d.cloudfront.net\\/CIK-0001045810\\/6314522a-929c-470d-b67c-23fa99238516.pdf\\\" class=\\\"ssrcss-k17ofw-InlineLink e1kn3p7n0\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: none; border-left: 0px; border-image: initial; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: underline 1px rgb(138, 140, 142); text-decoration-skip-ink: none; text-underline-offset: 0.25em;\\\">has said in a filing<\\/a>&nbsp;that the new export restrictions will block sales of two high-end artificial intelligence chips it created for the Chinese market - A800 and H800. It said that one of its gaming chips will also be blocked.<\\/span><\\/p><\\/div><\\/div><div data-component=\\\"text-block\\\" class=\\\"ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\\\" style=\\\"margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem;\\\"><div class=\\\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\\\"><p class=\\\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\\\" style=\\\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color: rgb(206, 198, 206);\\\">Although the curbs also affect other chip makers, analysts believe Nvidia will be hit the hardest because China accounts for up to 25% of its revenues from data centre chip sales. Nvidia\'s shares, which are considered a star stock, fell by as much as 4.7% in the wake of the announcement.<\\/span><\\/p><\\/div><\\/div><div id=\\\"piano-inline1\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\\\"><\\/div><div data-component=\\\"text-block\\\" class=\\\"ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\\\" style=\\\"margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem;\\\"><div class=\\\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\\\"><p class=\\\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\\\" style=\\\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color: rgb(206, 198, 206);\\\">The Semiconductor Industry Association, which represents 99% of the US semiconductor industry by revenue, said in&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.semiconductors.org\\/sia-statement-on-new-export-controls-2\\/\\\" class=\\\"ssrcss-k17ofw-InlineLink e1kn3p7n0\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: none; border-left: 0px; border-image: initial; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: underline 1px rgb(138, 140, 142); text-decoration-skip-ink: none; text-underline-offset: 0.25em;\\\">a statement<\\/a>&nbsp;that the new measures are \\\"overly broad\\\" and \\\"risk harming the US semiconductor ecosystem without advancing national security as they encourage overseas customers to look elsewhere\\\".<\\/span><\\/p><\\/div><\\/div><div data-component=\\\"text-block\\\" class=\\\"ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\\\" style=\\\"margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem;\\\"><div class=\\\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\\\"><p class=\\\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\\\" style=\\\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color: rgb(206, 198, 206);\\\">A spokesperson for the Chinese embassy also said that it \\\"firmly opposes\\\" the new restrictions, which also target Iran and Russia and go into effect in 30 days.<\\/span><\\/p><\\/div><\\/div><div data-component=\\\"text-block\\\" class=\\\"ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\\\" style=\\\"margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem;\\\"><div class=\\\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\\\"><p class=\\\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\\\" style=\\\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color: rgb(206, 198, 206);\\\">Two months ago, China retaliated by&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.bbc.com\\/news\\/business-66118831\\\" class=\\\"ssrcss-k17ofw-InlineLink e1kn3p7n0\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: none; border-left: 0px; border-image: initial; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: underline 1px rgb(138, 140, 142); text-decoration-skip-ink: none; text-underline-offset: 0.25em;\\\">restricting exports of two materials<\\/a>, gallium and germanium, which are key to the semiconductor industry.<\\/span><\\/p><\\/div><\\/div><div data-component=\\\"text-block\\\" class=\\\"ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\\\" style=\\\"margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem;\\\"><div class=\\\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\\\"><p class=\\\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\\\" style=\\\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color: rgb(206, 198, 206);\\\">China is by far the biggest player in the global supply chain of gallium and germanium. It produces 80% of the world\'s gallium and 60% of germanium, according to the Critical Raw Materials Alliance (CRMA) industry body.<\\/span><\\/p><\\/div><\\/div><div data-component=\\\"text-block\\\" class=\\\"ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\\\" style=\\\"margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem;\\\"><div class=\\\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\\\"><p class=\\\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\\\" style=\\\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color: rgb(206, 198, 206);\\\">The materials are \\\"minor metals\\\", meaning that they are not usually found on their own in nature, and are often the by-product of other processes.<\\/span><\\/p><\\/div><\\/div><div data-component=\\\"text-block\\\" class=\\\"ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\\\" style=\\\"margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem;\\\"><div class=\\\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\\\"><p class=\\\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\\\" style=\\\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color: rgb(206, 198, 206);\\\">Besides the US, both Japan and the Netherlands - which is home to key chip equipment maker ASML - have also imposed chip technology export restrictions on China.<\\/span><\\/p><\\/div><\\/div><div id=\\\"piano-inline2\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\\\"><\\/div><div data-component=\\\"text-block\\\" class=\\\"ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\\\" style=\\\"margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem;\\\"><div class=\\\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\\\"><p class=\\\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\\\" style=\\\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color: rgb(206, 198, 206);\\\">The constant tit-for-tat between the world\'s two biggest economies has raised concerns over the rise of so-called \\\"resource nationalism\\\" when governments hoard critical materials to exert influence over other countries.<\\/span><\\/p><\\/div><\\/div>\"}}', NULL, '2023-10-20 19:32:45', '2023-10-20 19:32:45');
