(2, 'India aims to send astronaut to the Moon by 2040', 'india-aims-to-send-astronaut-to-the-moon-by-2040', 'India aims to send astronaut to the Moon by 2040', '<div data-component=\"text-block\" class=\"ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\" style=\"margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\"><div class=\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">The country\'s space goals also include plans for a space station by 2035.</p></div></div><div data-component=\"text-block\" class=\"ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\" style=\"margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\"><div class=\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Prime Minister Narendra Modi announced these ambitions on Tuesday, and also asked scientists to work on missions to Venus and Mars.</p></div></div><div data-component=\"text-block\" class=\"ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\" style=\"margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\"><div class=\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">In August, India became the first country to&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-india-66594520\" class=\"ssrcss-k17ofw-InlineLink e1kn3p7n0\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: none; border-left: 0px; border-image: initial; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(20, 20, 20); text-decoration: underline 1px rgb(138, 140, 142); text-decoration-skip-ink: none; text-underline-offset: 0.25em;\">land a spacecraft on the Moon\'s south pole</a>, and in September it launched a rocket to study the Sun.</p></div></div><div data-component=\"text-block\" class=\"ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\" style=\"margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\"><div class=\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">The Indian Space Research Organisation (Isro) is also working on the Gaganyaan project, which aims to send a human crew to an orbit of 400km (248 miles) and bring them back safely to land in Indian waters. On Saturday, the space agency will conduct a key test in the mission.</p></div></div><div data-component=\"text-block\" class=\"ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\" style=\"margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\"><div class=\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">This will be be followed by another test flight carrying a robot to outer space before the final manned mission takes place before the end of 2024.</p></div></div>', 'Article', 1, 'Technology', 1, '/storage/photos/1/652fc1df6b271.webp', NULL, 'India Aims To Send Astronaut To The Moon By 2040', NULL, '', '/storage/photos/1/652fc1df6b271.webp', NULL, 2, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, 1, 'Super Admin', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-10-18 11:31:00', '2023-10-18 12:38:09', '2023-10-27 14:19:32', NULL),
