(5, 'US-China chip war: Nvidia hit as China cut off from more advanced chips', 'us-china-chip-war:-nvidia-hit-as-china-cut-off-from-more-advanced-chips', 'US-China chip war: Nvidia hit as China cut off from more advanced chips', '<div data-component=\"text-block\" class=\"ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\" style=\"margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\"><div class=\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b class=\"ssrcss-hmf8ql-BoldText e5tfeyi3\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">The Biden administration&nbsp;</b><a href=\"https://www.bis.doc.gov/index.php/about-bis/newsroom/2082?ref=upstract.com\" class=\"ssrcss-k17ofw-InlineLink e1kn3p7n0\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: none; border-left: 0px; border-image: initial; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(20, 20, 20); text-decoration: underline 1px rgb(138, 140, 142); text-decoration-skip-ink: none; text-underline-offset: 0.25em;\">has announced</a><b class=\"ssrcss-hmf8ql-BoldText e5tfeyi3\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">&nbsp;new restrictions on exports of advanced chips to China, including two made-for-China chips from Nvidia.</b></p></div></div><div data-component=\"text-block\" class=\"ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\" style=\"margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\"><div class=\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">US chip stocks fell as the curbs also hit Advanced Micro Devices and Intel.</p></div></div><div data-component=\"text-block\" class=\"ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\" style=\"margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\"><div class=\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">The curbs are aimed at closing loopholes that became apparent after&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/business-63175527\" class=\"ssrcss-k17ofw-InlineLink e1kn3p7n0\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: none; border-left: 0px; border-image: initial; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(20, 20, 20); text-decoration: underline 1px rgb(138, 140, 142); text-decoration-skip-ink: none; text-underline-offset: 0.25em;\">the US announced export curbs on chips last October</a>.</p></div></div><div data-component=\"text-block\" class=\"ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\" style=\"margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\"><div class=\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">They are designed to prevent China\'s military from importing advanced semiconductors or equipment.</p></div></div><div data-component=\"text-block\" class=\"ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\" style=\"margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\"><div class=\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Nvidia&nbsp;<a href=\"https://d18rn0p25nwr6d.cloudfront.net/CIK-0001045810/6314522a-929c-470d-b67c-23fa99238516.pdf\" class=\"ssrcss-k17ofw-InlineLink e1kn3p7n0\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: none; border-left: 0px; border-image: initial; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(20, 20, 20); text-decoration: underline 1px rgb(138, 140, 142); text-decoration-skip-ink: none; text-underline-offset: 0.25em;\">has said in a filing</a>&nbsp;that the new export restrictions will block sales of two high-end artificial intelligence chips it created for the Chinese market - A800 and H800. It said that one of its gaming chips will also be blocked.</p></div></div><div data-component=\"text-block\" class=\"ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\" style=\"margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\"><div class=\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Although the curbs also affect other chip makers, analysts believe Nvidia will be hit the hardest because China accounts for up to 25% of its revenues from data centre chip sales. Nvidia\'s shares, which are considered a star stock, fell by as much as 4.7% in the wake of the announcement.</p></div></div><div id=\"piano-inline1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\"></div><div data-component=\"text-block\" class=\"ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\" style=\"margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\"><div class=\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">The Semiconductor Industry Association, which represents 99% of the US semiconductor industry by revenue, said in&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.semiconductors.org/sia-statement-on-new-export-controls-2/\" class=\"ssrcss-k17ofw-InlineLink e1kn3p7n0\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: none; border-left: 0px; border-image: initial; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(20, 20, 20); text-decoration: underline 1px rgb(138, 140, 142); text-decoration-skip-ink: none; text-underline-offset: 0.25em;\">a statement</a>&nbsp;that the new measures are \"overly broad\" and \"risk harming the US semiconductor ecosystem without advancing national security as they encourage overseas customers to look elsewhere\".</p></div></div><div data-component=\"text-block\" class=\"ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\" style=\"margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\"><div class=\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">A spokesperson for the Chinese embassy also said that it \"firmly opposes\" the new restrictions, which also target Iran and Russia and go into effect in 30 days.</p></div></div><div data-component=\"text-block\" class=\"ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\" style=\"margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\"><div class=\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Two months ago, China retaliated by&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/business-66118831\" class=\"ssrcss-k17ofw-InlineLink e1kn3p7n0\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: none; border-left: 0px; border-image: initial; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(20, 20, 20); text-decoration: underline 1px rgb(138, 140, 142); text-decoration-skip-ink: none; text-underline-offset: 0.25em;\">restricting exports of two materials</a>, gallium and germanium, which are key to the semiconductor industry.</p></div></div><div data-component=\"text-block\" class=\"ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\" style=\"margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\"><div class=\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">China is by far the biggest player in the global supply chain of gallium and germanium. It produces 80% of the world\'s gallium and 60% of germanium, according to the Critical Raw Materials Alliance (CRMA) industry body.</p></div></div><div data-component=\"text-block\" class=\"ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\" style=\"margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\"><div class=\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">The materials are \"minor metals\", meaning that they are not usually found on their own in nature, and are often the by-product of other processes.</p></div></div><div data-component=\"text-block\" class=\"ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\" style=\"margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\"><div class=\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Besides the US, both Japan and the Netherlands - which is home to key chip equipment maker ASML - have also imposed chip technology export restrictions on China.</p></div></div><div id=\"piano-inline2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\"></div><div data-component=\"text-block\" class=\"ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\" style=\"margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\"><div class=\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">The constant tit-for-tat between the world\'s two biggest economies has raised concerns over the rise of so-called \"resource nationalism\" when governments hoard critical materials to exert influence over other countries.</p></div></div>', 'Article', 1, 'Technology', 1, '/storage/photos/1/652fc09b3e3f2.webp', NULL, 'US-China Chip War: Nvidia Hit As China Cut Off From More Advanced Chips', NULL, '', '/storage/photos/1/652fc09b3e3f2.webp', NULL, 14, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, 1, 'Super Admin', NULL, 1, NULL, '2023-10-18 11:27:00', '2023-10-18 12:27:42', '2023-11-04 21:10:47', NULL),
(6, 'India aims to send astronaut to the Moon by 2040', 'india-aims-to-send-astronaut-to-the-moon-by-2040', 'India aims to send astronaut to the Moon by 2040', '<div data-component=\"text-block\" class=\"ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\" style=\"margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\"><div class=\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">The country\'s space goals also include plans for a space station by 2035.</p></div></div><div data-component=\"text-block\" class=\"ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\" style=\"margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\"><div class=\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Prime Minister Narendra Modi announced these ambitions on Tuesday, and also asked scientists to work on missions to Venus and Mars.</p></div></div><div data-component=\"text-block\" class=\"ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\" style=\"margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\"><div class=\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">In August, India became the first country to&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-india-66594520\" class=\"ssrcss-k17ofw-InlineLink e1kn3p7n0\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: none; border-left: 0px; border-image: initial; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(20, 20, 20); text-decoration: underline 1px rgb(138, 140, 142); text-decoration-skip-ink: none; text-underline-offset: 0.25em;\">land a spacecraft on the Moon\'s south pole</a>, and in September it launched a rocket to study the Sun.</p></div></div><div data-component=\"text-block\" class=\"ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\" style=\"margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\"><div class=\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">The Indian Space Research Organisation (Isro) is also working on the Gaganyaan project, which aims to send a human crew to an orbit of 400km (248 miles) and bring them back safely to land in Indian waters. On Saturday, the space agency will conduct a key test in the mission.</p></div></div><div data-component=\"text-block\" class=\"ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\" style=\"margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\"><div class=\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">This will be be followed by another test flight carrying a robot to outer space before the final manned mission takes place before the end of 2024.</p></div></div>', 'Article', 1, 'Technology', 1, '/storage/photos/1/652fc1df6b271.webp', NULL, 'India Aims To Send Astronaut To The Moon By 2040', NULL, '', '/storage/photos/1/652fc1df6b271.webp', NULL, 1, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, 1, 'Super Admin', NULL, 1, NULL, '2023-10-18 11:31:00', '2023-10-18 12:38:09', '2023-10-18 12:45:50', NULL),
(7, 'US-China chip war: Nvidia hit as China cut off from more advanced chips', 'us-china-chip-war:-nvidia-hit-as-china-cut-off-from-more-advanced-chips', 'US-China chip war: Nvidia hit as China cut off from more advanced chips', '<div data-component=\"text-block\" class=\"ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\" style=\"margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\"><div class=\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b class=\"ssrcss-hmf8ql-BoldText e5tfeyi3\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">The Biden administration </b><a href=\"https://www.bis.doc.gov/index.php/about-bis/newsroom/2082?ref=upstract.com\" class=\"ssrcss-k17ofw-InlineLink e1kn3p7n0\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: none; border-left: 0px; border-image: initial; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(20, 20, 20); text-decoration: underline 1px rgb(138, 140, 142); text-decoration-skip-ink: none; text-underline-offset: 0.25em;\">has announced</a><b class=\"ssrcss-hmf8ql-BoldText e5tfeyi3\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"> new restrictions on exports of advanced chips to China, including two made-for-China chips from Nvidia.</b></p></div></div><div data-component=\"text-block\" class=\"ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\" style=\"margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\"><div class=\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">US chip stocks fell as the curbs also hit Advanced Micro Devices and Intel.</p></div></div><div data-component=\"text-block\" class=\"ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\" style=\"margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\"><div class=\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">The curbs are aimed at closing loopholes that became apparent after <a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/business-63175527\" class=\"ssrcss-k17ofw-InlineLink e1kn3p7n0\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: none; border-left: 0px; border-image: initial; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(20, 20, 20); text-decoration: underline 1px rgb(138, 140, 142); text-decoration-skip-ink: none; text-underline-offset: 0.25em;\">the US announced export curbs on chips last October</a>.</p></div></div><div data-component=\"text-block\" class=\"ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\" style=\"margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\"><div class=\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">They are designed to prevent China\'s military from importing advanced semiconductors or equipment.</p></div></div><div data-component=\"text-block\" class=\"ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\" style=\"margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\"><div class=\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Nvidia <a href=\"https://d18rn0p25nwr6d.cloudfront.net/CIK-0001045810/6314522a-929c-470d-b67c-23fa99238516.pdf\" class=\"ssrcss-k17ofw-InlineLink e1kn3p7n0\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: none; border-left: 0px; border-image: initial; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(20, 20, 20); text-decoration: underline 1px rgb(138, 140, 142); text-decoration-skip-ink: none; text-underline-offset: 0.25em;\">has said in a filing</a> that the new export restrictions will block sales of two high-end artificial intelligence chips it created for the Chinese market - A800 and H800. It said that one of its gaming chips will also be blocked.</p></div></div><div data-component=\"text-block\" class=\"ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\" style=\"margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\"><div class=\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Although the curbs also affect other chip makers, analysts believe Nvidia will be hit the hardest because China accounts for up to 25% of its revenues from data centre chip sales. Nvidia\'s shares, which are considered a star stock, fell by as much as 4.7% in the wake of the announcement.</p></div></div><div id=\"piano-inline1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\"></div><div data-component=\"text-block\" class=\"ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\" style=\"margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\"><div class=\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">The Semiconductor Industry Association, which represents 99% of the US semiconductor industry by revenue, said in <a href=\"https://www.semiconductors.org/sia-statement-on-new-export-controls-2/\" class=\"ssrcss-k17ofw-InlineLink e1kn3p7n0\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: none; border-left: 0px; border-image: initial; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(20, 20, 20); text-decoration: underline 1px rgb(138, 140, 142); text-decoration-skip-ink: none; text-underline-offset: 0.25em;\">a statement</a> that the new measures are \"overly broad\" and \"risk harming the US semiconductor ecosystem without advancing national security as they encourage overseas customers to look elsewhere\".</p></div></div><div data-component=\"text-block\" class=\"ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\" style=\"margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\"><div class=\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">A spokesperson for the Chinese embassy also said that it \"firmly opposes\" the new restrictions, which also target Iran and Russia and go into effect in 30 days.</p></div></div><div data-component=\"text-block\" class=\"ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\" style=\"margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\"><div class=\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Two months ago, China retaliated by <a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/business-66118831\" class=\"ssrcss-k17ofw-InlineLink e1kn3p7n0\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: none; border-left: 0px; border-image: initial; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(20, 20, 20); text-decoration: underline 1px rgb(138, 140, 142); text-decoration-skip-ink: none; text-underline-offset: 0.25em;\">restricting exports of two materials</a>, gallium and germanium, which are key to the semiconductor industry.</p></div></div><div data-component=\"text-block\" class=\"ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\" style=\"margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\"><div class=\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">China is by far the biggest player in the global supply chain of gallium and germanium. It produces 80% of the world\'s gallium and 60% of germanium, according to the Critical Raw Materials Alliance (CRMA) industry body.</p></div></div><div data-component=\"text-block\" class=\"ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\" style=\"margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\"><div class=\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">The materials are \"minor metals\", meaning that they are not usually found on their own in nature, and are often the by-product of other processes.</p></div></div><div data-component=\"text-block\" class=\"ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\" style=\"margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\"><div class=\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline